description.narrative:
The objectives of the intervention are the following:
1. Strengthen the planning and management of the national statistics system2. Contribute to further improve products and quality of priority statistics (economic, social and environmental statistics),3. Increase availability of data for decision making and monitoring of national and international development plans.
At the end of the intervention, the following specific results are expected:
-improvement  of the effectiveness of the production process and coordination mechanisms of the national statistics system;
-development of statistics on prices, companies et improvement of the quality of macro economical statistics according to international standards;
-improvement of the reach and quality of social statistics , including key SDG indicators to respond to user's needs;
-improvement of the reach and quality of agricultural and environmental statistics, including SDGs.
-better availability and friendly dissemination of statistics in accordance with user's needs
